  <h2>Import Summary</h2>
  <p>
    <b> Initial number of books in the database:</b>
    <span id="recordsInitial"></span>
  </p>
  <p><b> Books Inserted Successfully:</b> <span id="recordsInserted"></span></p>
  <p>
    <b> Resulting number of books in the database:</b>
    <span id="recordsProcessed"></span>
  </p>

  <h2>Error Summary</h2>
  <p>
    <b> Total Book Records Processed:</b> <span id="recordsProcessed"></span>
  </p>
  <p><b> Number of Books Not Inserted:</b> <span id="recordsFailed"></span></p>
  <p><b> Errors: </b></p>
  <p id="errorList"></p>
</div>
